## Key design decisions (see docs/pipeline_architecture.md)
- $0 cost: local Whisper + Gemini free tier
- Postgres over MongoDB (relational queries, materialized views)
- Separate container from work DB (port 25433 vs 25432)
- Frames on filesystem, metadata in Postgres
- Materialized views for agent runtime, never query raw tables
